title: El Sistema Sweden National Orchestra
text:
The El Sistema Sweden National Orchestra (Swedish: El Sistema Nationalorkester) is the national youth orchestra of Sweden. Founded in 2019 by El Sistema Sweden and STIM, it consists of students of age 11 to 19 from all over Sweden. It is supported by the Royal Stockholm Philharmonic Orchestra and the Swedish Radio Symphony Orchestra.
